Àtụ:Infobox Airport
Goodnews Airport (: GNU,  : ) bụ ọdụ ụgbọ elu ọha na eze nke dị na Goodnews Bay na Betel Census Area nke steeti Alaska dị na United States.
Dịka ndekọ Federal Aviation Administration si kwuo, ọdụ ụgbọ elu a nwere ndị njem azụmahịa nke rụrụ Otú nde, puku narị ise iri atọ na abụọ
(enplanements) n'afọ kalenda 2008, mbelata nke 2.2% site na  Otú nde, puku narị ise, iri isii na asaa  n'afọ 2007
A na-etinye ọdụ ụgbọ elu Goodnews na atụmatụ mba FAA nke Integrated Airport Systems (2009-2013), nke na-ekewa ya dịka ụlọ ọrụ ụgbọ elu n'ozuzu.
Ọdụ ụgbọ elu Goodnews nwere otu ụzọ ụgbọ elu a kpọrọ 5/23 nke nwere ala gravelu  nke na-atụle otú nde, narị asotọ, Iri atọ na ise, site na  ndanye iri asatọ (864 x 24 m)

N'ime ọnwa iri na abụọ nke gwụchara na n'abalị iri atọ na otu nke Julaị,  n'afọ 2006, ọdụ ụgbọ elu ahụ nwere ọrụ ụgbọ elu puku atọ na narị iri abụọ nkezi nke otu narị, Ịrị isii na isii kwa ọnwa: 62.5% ụgbọ elu na 37.5% ụgbọelu
National Geodetic Survey enyochaala ọdụ ụgbọ elu a.
Ụzọ ụgbọelu  na ebe aga eru
